# {{PROJECT_NAME}} - Mock Data Guide

**Purpose:** Guide for implementing mock data and API stubs for development and testing without a real backend.

---

## Overview

This guide provides a system for mock data and API stub endpoints that allow you to develop and test the UI without needing a real backend.

---

