## Configuration

### Environment Variables

```bash
# .env.local

# Real API URL (optional, uses mock if not set)
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.{{PROJECT_SLUG}}.com/v1

# Force mock mode (true/false)
NEXT_PUBLIC_USE_MOCK=true
```

### Automatic Mock Mode

The system automatically uses mock data when:
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` is not defined
- `NEXT_PUBLIC_USE_MOCK=true`

