## API Endpoints

### GET /api/[endpoint1]

```bash
curl http://localhost:3000/api/[endpoint1]
```

**Response:**
```json
{
  "data": {
    "period": { "start": "...", "end": "...", "label": "Current Period" },
    "total[Entity]": 0,
    "total[Unit]": 0,
    "totalAmount": 0,
    "average[metric]": 0,
    "successRate": 0,
    "top[Entities]": [...],
    "dailyBreakdown": [...]
  }
}
```

### GET /api/[endpoint2]

```bash
curl "http://localhost:3000/api/[endpoint2]?limit=10&filter=value"
```

### GET /api/[endpoint3]

```bash
curl http://localhost:3000/api/[endpoint3]/[id]
```

### POST /api/[endpoint4]

```bash
curl -X POST http://localhost:3000/api/[endpoint4] \
  -H "Content-Type: application/json" \
  -d '{"key": "value"}'
```

