## Migration to Real Backend

### Step 1: Configure API URL

```bash
# .env.local
NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL=https://api.{{PROJECT_SLUG}}.com/v1
NEXT_PUBLIC_USE_MOCK=false
```

### Step 2: Update Endpoints

Replace mocks in each route handler:

```typescript
// app/api/[endpoint]/route.ts

// BEFORE (mock):
import { [ENTITY] } from '@/data/mocks';
return NextResponse.json({ data: [ENTITY] });

// AFTER (real):
import { db } from '@/lib/db';
const result = await db.query('SELECT * FROM [table]...');
return NextResponse.json({ data: result });
```

### Step 3: Update API Client

The `lib/api/client.ts` is already prepared to switch automatically when `NEXT_PUBLIC_API_URL` is defined.

